text:
OOXML Excel files store strings in a separate document which is shared by all
sheets. Extractors should be able to dereference strings from that document.
creator: ugo@apache.org
ugo@apache.org
text:
Created attachment 21357
Partial fix

Partial implementation of shared strings support.
Has got workaround for possible XMLBeans bug, uses DOM to parse shared strings
document instead of XMLBeans.
